[02:10.19]	The silence often of pure innocence
[02:12.99]	Persuades when speaking fails.
[02:15.40]EMILIA	Most worthy madam,
[02:17.00]	Your honour and your goodness is so evident
[02:20.34]	That your free undertaking cannot miss
[02:23.35]	A thriving issue: there is no lady living
[02:26.49]	So meet for this great errand. Please your ladyship
[02:30.30]	To visit the next room, I'll presently
[02:33.24]	Acquaint the queen of your most noble offer;
